Eury 12/29/2025:

1. New Features Added
Edit Functionality (Update): Users can now click a "Pencil" icon to modify an existing recordâ€™s details (Title, Sponsor, etc.) or replace the uploaded file entirely.

Delete Functionality (Delete): Users can click a "Trash" icon to permanently remove a record from both the Database and Storage.

File Validation: Restricted uploads to only allow PDF, DOC, and DOCX files, blocking images or other types.

Expiry Date: Added a new column and data field to track when an ordinance or resolution expires.

Empty State: Improved the table so it looks good even when there is no data (shows a "No records found" message).

2. Files Created & Modified
A. New File Created
src/components/Modal/EditRecordModal.jsx: A new modal component that pre-fills with existing data and allows users to save changes or replace the document.

B. Files Modified
