Added handleEditClick and handleUpdateRecord functions.

Implemented logic to upload a replacement file if the user selects a new one during editing.

Added the logic to delete the raw file object from the data before saving to preventing database crashes.

Connected the Edit Modal to the page.

src/components/Main/MainTable.jsx

Added the Pencil (Edit) and Trash (Delete) icons.

Implemented handleDelete to remove data from Firestore and Storage.

Updated to accept and use the onEdit prop.

Added the Expiry Date column.

